    "description": "<br><br><strong>EMPTY SHELL: THE LOOP 是对原版 EMPTY SHELL 游戏玩法的不同诠释。</strong><br><br>你将被扔进“环路”，这是一个建在日本荒岛上的秘密设施。 志愿者被迫进入建筑群的怪异房间，似乎没有出口。 但其中一个房间里那扇巨大的门是什么？ 也许有办法逃脱吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/250172b1dbb391cd34baabc09c9172b5.poster.avif?t=1728000564\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/250172b1dbb391cd34baabc09c9172b5.webm?t=1728000564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/250172b1dbb391cd34baabc09c9172b5.mp4?t=1728000564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在黑白俯视视角的镜头下，你将控制一名志愿者，在他死后，你会控制另一个，再控制另一个。你将与成群的畸形怪物战斗，试图一个房间接一个房间地前进.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/b05df090a9a4aed9348f2754bdef26af.poster.avif?t=1728000564\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/b05df090a9a4aed9348f2754bdef26af.webm?t=1728000564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/b05df090a9a4aed9348f2754bdef26af.mp4?t=1728000564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>揭示“循环”建设背后的秘密以及整个项目。解锁新武器、装备、设备，并用新的技能提升志愿者的实力，增加逃生的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/9f6ad56762de2ef1005709b7908f5113.poster.avif?t=1728000564\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/9f6ad56762de2ef1005709b7908f5113.webm?t=1728000564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023390/extras/9f6ad56762de2ef1005709b7908f5113.mp4?t=1728000564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在循环中一房间接一房间地与被困其中的可怕怪物作战<br></li><li>购买新装备并打造您喜爱的构建<br></li><li>解锁全新技能并提升志愿者的实力以增加逃生的机会<br></li><li>在死亡前赚取积分并将其转移以支持未来的志愿者<br></li><li>在奔跑中升级您的武器并增加火力<br></li><li>访问终端并揭示“循环”创建背后的黑暗动机</li></ul>",
